'''Linopristin''' is an [[antibiotic]] of the [[streptogramin B]] class. It is one of the components of the antibiotic combination [[NXL103]].<ref>{{cite journal | author = Pankuch, Glenn A.; Kelly, Linda M.; Lin, Gengrong; Bryskier, Andre; Couturier, Catherine; Jacobs, Michael R.; Appelbaum, Peter C. | title = Activities of a new oral streptogramin, XRP 2868, compared to those of other agents against Streptococcus pneumoniae and Haemophilus species | journal = Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy | year = 2003 | volume = 47 | issue = 10 | pages = 3270–3274 | doi = 10.1128/AAC.47.10.3270-3274.2003 | pmid = 14506040 | pmc = 201162}}</ref>
