'''Validamycin''' is an [[antibiotic]] and [[fungicide]] produced by ''[[Streptomyces hygroscopicus]]''. It is used as an inhibitor of [[trehalase]].<ref>{{cite pmid | 22036231}}</ref> It is used for the control of sheath blight of rice and damping-off of cucumbers.
